 Fubon Financial Holding Co. Logo
Fubon Financial Holding Co., Ltd. is a financial investment holding company consists of the following key subsidiaries : Fubon Asset Management, Fubon Insurance Co. Ltd., Fubon Securities, Fubon Bank, Fubon Life and Fubon Bank Limited. The holding company was setup on 19 December 2001. Fubon FHC has its headquarters in Taipei. Fubon Group’s logo compresses “Fubon” to “FB” and uses two thick lines to spell “FB.”
